Dimensions.s2cor__Description__c: Click here to see a list of your Products.  Sage Live Products can be linked with Salesforce Products.  You can create a new Product by clicking on the plus symbol.

Dimensions.Name: Project
Dimensions.s2cor__Description__c: Click here to see a list of your Projects.   You can create a new Project by clicking on the plus symbol.

Dimensions.Name: Revenue
Dimensions.s2cor__Description__c: List of Revenue sources used in budget, forecast and bank receipts journals.

Dimensions.Name: Supplier
Dimensions.s2cor__Description__c: Click here to see a list of your Suppliers and their current balances.  Sage Live Supplier records can be linked to Salesforce Accounts to give a complete view of your Supplier. You can create a new Sage Live Supplier by clicking on the plus symbol.
